      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink34">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi nammūrp</l>
          <l> poykaip pūtta puḻaikkā lāmpaṟ</l>
          <l> ṟātēr vaṇṇaṅ koṇṭaṉa</l>
          <l> vētilā ḷarkkup pacantaveṉ kaṇṇē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">

          <l> Alas, [my] friend!</l>
          <l> My eyes that went pale for a stranger</l>
          <l> have taken on a colour like the pollen </l>
          <l> of the hollow-stalked white lotus that flowered in the pond</l> 
          <l> in our village.</l>
         


        </lg>
      </div>
